Palma Says Markets to Stay `Sideways' Amid Europe Crisis

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-28T15:34:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/palma-says-markets-to-stay-sideways-amid-europe-crisis-video.html
Jeffrey Palma, global equity 
strategist at UBS Securities LLC, discusses Europe's debt 
crisis and it's potential impact on global markets.   Palma, speaking with Betty Liu, Jon Erlichman and Dominic 
Chu on Bloomberg Television's "In the Loop," also talks about 
the outlook for the Standard & Poor's 500 Index and valuations 
for technology companies. Nicholas Thompson, senior editor at 
the New Yorker magazine and a Bloomberg Television contributing 
editor, also speaks. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 09:44
 